playstore_details.title: IDProve OTP
playstore_details.description:
Gemalto’s IDProve 300 one-touch user experience for strong authentication allows businesses to leverage the security of one-time passwords (OTPs) using mobile phones. 
Gemalto’s IDConfirm & IDProve solutions help to deploy strong authentication to internal and Cloud resources.
